:::mg car survival:::

    - The map supports only 24 people/slots

    - There are 5 levels of difficulty   

    - Music that plays in the background


#### Newer Version!
- [V2](http://www.gamebanana.com/css/maps/164420 "V2")
- [V3](http://www.gamebanana.com/css/maps/164686 "V3")


==What's the point of the map?==


*Basically you need to dodge the cars without being hit by one of them to survival and win.



Enjoy!

Your feedback is important for me,so comment your thoughts about the map!


Map by DmgVol.
